{"word":"G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee' - Am","slug":"G1510","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἰμί</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>eimí"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>i-mee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Am"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0313;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x0301; - eimi</b> - <i>i-mee'</i><p/>First person singular present indicative; a prolonged form of a primary and defective verb; I <i>exist</i> (used only when emphatic): - am, have been, X it is I, was. See also <a href=\"#/G1488\">G1488</a>, <a href=\"#/G1498\">G1498</a>, <a href=\"#/G1511\">G1511</a>, <a href=\"#/G1527\">G1527</a>, <a href=\"#/G2258\">G2258</a>, <a href=\"#/G2071\">G2071</a>, <a href=\"#/G2070\">G2070</a>, <a href=\"#/G2075\">G2075</a>, <a href=\"#/G2076\">G2076</a>, <a href=\"#/G2771\">G2771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2468\">G2468</a>, <a href=\"#/G5600\">G5600</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5607\">G5607</a>"}]}